    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard Wizards</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Type. Cast. Conquer!</strong></h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Keyboard Wizards</strong> is a fast-paced, magic-infused card battler where every spell is cast by your typing skill! Build your spell deck, unleash powerful magic, and test your reflexes in battles inspired by Philippine folklore.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧙‍♂️ <strong>Become the best Keyboard Wizard!</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unique Typing Combat:</strong> Cast spells and attack enemies by typing magic incantations—speed and accuracy mean victory!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/c3d1d2ff975a5759c47bfd7b4e6c688e.poster.avif?t=1747995434\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/c3d1d2ff975a5759c47bfd7b4e6c688e.webm?t=1747995434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/c3d1d2ff975a5759c47bfd7b4e6c688e.mp4?t=1747995434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Build Your Spell Deck:</strong> Collect and customize spell cards, discover powerful combos, and create your winning strategy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/0b3b6ac405cfb00424f7fe3a7ae0801a.avif?t=1747995434\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras_big/0b3b6ac405cfb00424f7fe3a7ae0801a.avif?t=1747995434 width=800 height=450 /></span><br></li><li><strong>Epic Fantasy Battles:</strong> Duel deadly AI opponents in magical arenas inspired by creatures and legends from the Philippines.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/ed8c6674f5587314532700b318ff77d9.poster.avif?t=1747995434\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/ed8c6674f5587314532700b318ff77d9.webm?t=1747995434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/ed8c6674f5587314532700b318ff77d9.mp4?t=1747995434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Status Effects &amp; Strategy:</strong> Heal, Stun, shield, or outwit your foes—timing your typing can mean the difference between victory and defeat!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/d701aea3e6ee92b540d991c0927eb43e.avif?t=1747995434\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras_big/d701aea3e6ee92b540d991c0927eb43e.avif?t=1747995434 width=800 height=450 /></span><br></li><li><strong>Fantasy Narrative or PvP Combat:</strong> Live the story of a new student to SIERRA ENCANTADA INSTITUTE of MAGICAL STUDIES as they rise to become the top wizard—or dominate PvP combat with your typing skills!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/992b90d4e454bf8a95923b1449ecc611.poster.avif?t=1747995434\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/992b90d4e454bf8a95923b1449ecc611.webm?t=1747995434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338850/extras/992b90d4e454bf8a95923b1449ecc611.mp4?t=1747995434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
